Michele Ragusa https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Michele_Ragusa 0 Michele Ragusa is an American actress and singer currently residing in New Jersey. She is best known for her work in Broadway Musicals and her solo performances and staged concerts with Symphony Orchestras around the United States. She also played a recurring role on the television comedy Happyish. Michele_Ragusa is an_American_actress_and_singer currently_residing in New_Jersey .
